author: Jason Smith
title: Memphis Madness FanFest details finalized
text:
The 2015 Memphis Madness FanFest will begin at 12:30 p.m. Saturday at FedExForum and include autograph sessions with the Tigers men's and women's basketball teams.
The FanFest will be preceded by a men's basketball season ticket Select-A-Seat event that begins at 10:30 a.m. and runs through noon.
The Memphis women's basketball team will sign autographs from 11 a.m. until noon on FedExForum's front outdoor plaza.
The men's team will be available for autographs and pictures starting at 1:30 p.m. on the FedExForum court. The event will also include clinic stations on the court with both the men's and women's teams.
